 tour website with the our Authorize.Net WordPress plugin and offer a wide range of payment options to your online customers for booking your trip and travel packages. This WP Travel payment add-on makes collecting payments through credit cards quick and painless. It can accept international payments from anywhere in the world as long as your tour business is based in the United Kingdom, United States, Canada, Europe or Australia.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress RazorPay Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> RazorPay is a popular payment gateway in India. Install RazorPay payment gateway in seconds using our plugin and enable the ability to receive international payments in India for tour bookings from anywhere around the globe.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Stripe WordPress Plugin:<\\/strong> Stripe is one of the largest payment companies in the world which processes payments of multiple sources. Along with it also offers a secure and seamless environment for users and merchants to do online transactions. With all the coding done, you can download and install this plugin on your site in a fly!\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress Instamojo Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> Instamojo payment gateway is one of the most popular payment options used by online platforms across the world. Our Instamojo payment plugin for WordPress offers easy-to-install and easy-to-use payment options for end users and travel site owners for process credit card, debit card, net banking payments, among others.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress Khalti Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> For Nepali travel agencies, the Khalti WordPress plugin is a savior. It allows users to book and pay for their trips using the Khalti payment gateway. With multiple payment options like debit cards of various Nepali banks, Khalti wallets, and e-banking payments, this plugin accepts all the local payments in Nepali rupees for Nepali travel and tour websites.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"19.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 14923,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-payfast-checkout\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel PayFast Checkout\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-05-17 12:27:00\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-02 07:51:17\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=14923\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-14977 size-full\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/05\\/featured-image-2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1920\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/themepalace.com\\/downloads\\/wp-travel-payfast-checkout\\\">WP Travel PayFast Checkout<\\/a> plugin is an on-demand payment option now available as a payment gateway for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/\\\">WP travel<\\/a> plugin which provides easy payment options for travel business based on South Africa. This payment gateway only works with the South African currency Rand (zar).\\r\\n<blockquote><em>*This payment gateway add-on is exclusively designed to work only with South African currency Rand (zar). And this ONLY works in conjunction with our parent plugin <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">WP Travel<\\/a> plugin installed, it does not work as a stand-alone plugin. If you haven\\u2019t installed this travel site plugin, download it <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel\\/\\\">here<\\/a> now- it\\u2019s totally FREE.<\\/em><\\/blockquote>\\r\\n<strong>Major Features:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Payment Gateway powering the customers of South Africa (Valid currency is zar)<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nPayFast is our recommended payments processing service for South Africans and South African websites. Their payment gateway offers a secure and instant transfer of money between online buyers and sellers. Merchants can accept funds from local and international customers from anywhere in the world in ZAR.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Connecting the sellers and buyers on a single platform with multiple ways to pay<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWith this extension, your trip bookers can experience a seamless payment transaction without having to leave the site once they enter the payment process. This feature makes the payment system look more trustworthy and provide customers with a smooth experience with your website.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Enable easy, secure and instant transfer of money between online buyers and sellers<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel PayFast Checkout provides a highly secure link with customizable security settings that fights fraud resulting in one of the most robust security you\\u2019ll find with payments, no better feeling than knowing your money is safe, isn\\u2019t it?\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Accepts Credit Card payment via visa and mastercard<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel PayFast Checkout provides you with multiple choices to make payments online including Mastercard, Visa card and direct bank transaction. This makes it a lot more convenient for a wide range of people to use this add-on.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Get 24\\/7 Support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nOur wonderful and knowledgeable support team loves to personally help you with every question about the plugin you ask through\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/support-forum\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">support forum<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Knowledge Base<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/category\\/knowledge-base\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Knowledge base<\\/a>\\u00a0is always a good place to start if you have a problem or a question about one of our plugins. You can check the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-payfast-checkout\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">documentation<\\/a>\\u00a0and other lists of articles, or easily search the Knowledge base to find the answers you\\u2019re looking for.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/05\\/wptravel-payfast-checkout.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 166,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 166,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2670,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Payment Plugins &amp; Gateways For Travel &amp; Tour Websites\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-travel-site-payment-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2670,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"<strong>Payment Plugins for WordPress Travel Sites<\\/strong>\\r\\nAbility to accept online payment is an important feature of the modern businesses. This is crucial for business that cater to worldwide audiences, like travel and tour sites. Having the ability for the user to instantly pay for their travel and tour bookings can be a great feature for the end users to use. And for the business, this could mean getting paid by users and getting real paid customers. But for developers or site owners integrating even the widely available payment gateways like PayPal, Authorize.net, can be a serious pain.\\r\\n\\r\\nAt WP Travel, we take this pain out of your schedule. We offer plugins for most of the widely used payment gateways around the world. These WordPress payment plugins are EXCLUSIVELY developed to work with WP Travel and are ONLY for travel and tour websites built on WordPress. Here are some of our most popular payment plugins for travel and tour websites on WordPress:\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>PayPal Checkout WordPress Plugin:<\\/strong> When it comes to online payment, PayPal by far is one of the most popular choices. Going one step ahead, the PayPal WordPress Checkout plugin helps you install the payment gateway on your travel website without the need for you to write even a single line of code. Just download and install WP Travel PayPal Checkout Plugin and let your users pay you from anywhere in the world.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress Authorize.Net Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> Power your travel and tour website with the our Authorize.Net WordPress plugin and offer a wide range of payment options to your online customers for booking your trip and travel packages. This WP Travel payment add-on makes collecting payments through credit cards quick and painless. It can accept international payments from anywhere in the world as long as your tour business is based in the United Kingdom, United States, Canada, Europe or Australia.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress RazorPay Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> RazorPay is a popular payment gateway in India. Install RazorPay payment gateway in seconds using our plugin and enable the ability to receive international payments in India for tour bookings from anywhere around the globe.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Stripe WordPress Plugin:<\\/strong> Stripe is one of the largest payment companies in the world which processes payments of multiple sources. Along with it also offers a secure and seamless environment for users and merchants to do online transactions. With all the coding done, you can download and install this plugin on your site in a fly!\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress Instamojo Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> Instamojo payment gateway is one of the most popular payment options used by online platforms across the world. Our Instamojo payment plugin for WordPress offers easy-to-install and easy-to-use payment options for end users and travel site owners for process credit card, debit card, net banking payments, among others.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress Khalti Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> For Nepali travel agencies, the Khalti WordPress plugin is a savior. It allows users to book and pay for their trips using the Khalti payment gateway. With multiple payment options like debit cards of various Nepali banks, Khalti wallets, and e-banking payments, this plugin accepts all the local payments in Nepali rupees for Nepali travel and tour websites.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"19.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 12906,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-group-discount\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Group Discount\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-04-11 10:16:19\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-09-23 09:08:32\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=12906\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"wp-image-12907 size-full aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/group-discount-banner.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1497\\\" height=\\\"614\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel group discounts has the ability to give discount based on user\\u2019s group. You will be able to add the price based on the no of people attending the trips.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Features<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Discounts offered to the users on flat discount basis:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13466 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/wp-travel-group-discounts-offered-to-the-users.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>Basically, the site will not be making any extra hidden money with the use of heavy discount numbers and hidden terms but flat discount can be given with respect to the user\\u2019s final payment, with absolutely no fake promises and hidden costs.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Allows the admin to add the discount amount from the backend:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13467 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/wp-travel-allows-the-admin-to-add-the-discount-amount-from-the-backend.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe discount percentage does not have to be computer set limits for a certain number of people, the site admin can manually choose how much discount can be offered to a particular user taking into consideration a lot of factors of their relevance and convenience.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Discount offered based on user group:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13468 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/wp-travel-discount-offered-based-on-user-group.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nSince the discount will be based for each different user based on the user group, this feature can prove to be a little push which will eventually help the business owner get a lot of group reservations, great for a travel business, isn\\u2019t it?\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/wp-travel-group-discount-thumbnail.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2017,\n                        \"name\": \"Miscellaneous\",\n                        \"slug\": \"miscellaneous\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2017,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"15.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 12621,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-downloads\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Downloads\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-04-02 08:14:32\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-09-23 09:12:13\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=12621\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12664 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/download-banner-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1497\\\" height=\\\"614\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWhen it comes to traveling or trekking, your visuals speak volume to your visitors than your words. As such it is not a coincidence that most of the travel and trekking sites have great pictures and videos on site. As a response, we developed this smart plugin that allows you to upload and manage your visuals just the way you want. Upload and present images and other media related to a package and provide your visitors the ability to download these materials with just one click.\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Downloads plugin provides travel site owners the ability to upload and attach digital media files associated with particular trips and destinations. It provides the users at the other end the facility to download those files from the webpage easily. This add-on is lightweight and makes uploading and downloading easier for everyone.\\r\\n\\r\\nThis plugin is built to let the travel site owner manage, track and control file downloads on their WordPress site. It is capable of uploading images, video, pdf, and other multimedia formats and creating special pages for each of these files including providing the ability to preview the files before downloading them.\\r\\n\\r\\nAlong with that, travel agency owners can manage all their multimedia visuals from their dashboard including the ability to upload new content, see the details of the files its type, the size on the disk and the ability to add a caption and other attributes to the file.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe plugin offers you dozens of translations and integrates with Google applications easily. You can organize your media files into categories and can easily access relevant files promptly from the dashboard without any friction.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>What do you need to install?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nAs the WP Travel Downloads add-on works only with WP Travel plugin, first install the WP Travel plugin and integrate the WP Travel Downloads add-on following the complete installation process click<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-downloads\\/\\\"> here<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Features of WP Travel Download Add-on\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Flaunt your offerings in multimedia format <\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nUpload and showcase all your multimedia information on your travel or trekking packages by using this plugin. This plugin helps you make your trekking and travel packages richer in terms of media usage. Get better attention and trust among your visitors and convert them into your customers- After all seeing is believing, show off your achievements using this addon!\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Upload anything that makes sense<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nNot just photos, this add-on lets you upload other digital documents like Trip brochures, videos, CSV, documents, e-books, songs, graphics, or any other type of media file that provides information to your visitor about your business or a particular travel package and thereby positively enhances your travel package sales.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Design to sync &amp; respond <\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe add on comes with highly flexible and responsive design capabilities. You can adjust it to suit the need and requirements of your travel site. This add-on complements to the aesthetics of your website and adds to the\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-downloads\\/#doc-client-side-10\\\">value of your trip details<\\/a>\\u00a0page by providing a better and clear picture of your travel packages to your visitors.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Upload any trip-related documents<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWith the larger space, you can upload any trips related documents in your travel site. Make your trip more promising by uploading different format documents like PDF, DOC, video, brochure and much more. With this, you can gain attention and trust among your travel visitors.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt is very important for your website to be visual-oriented and providing all the important documents and multimedia resources that they can access without going through a lot of trouble. Make it easy for by installing the WP Travel Download addon today. Go on click on the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/themepalace.com\\/download-checkout\\/?edd_action=add_to_cart&amp;download_id=93970\\\">Buy Now<\\/a> button below to download it now or head onto the<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-downloads\\/\\\"> documentation section<\\/a> learn how to install it and if you have any presale questions <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/contact\\/\\\">visit our contact page<\\/a> now.\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/download.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2017,\n                        \"name\": \"Miscellaneous\",\n                        \"slug\": \"miscellaneous\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2017,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"15.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 12512,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-mailchimp\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel MailChimp\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-03-25 11:53:59\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-02 10:39:02\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=12512\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-12643\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/mail-chimp-main-banner-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1497\\\" height=\\\"614\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nTrying to boost the conversion rate for travel booking packages? Then install our MailChimp WordPress plugin on your WordPress tour website. WP Travel MailChimp is one of the best additions to our WP Travel plugin to create, manage and analyze your email campaign within minutes. Powered by MailChimp, a global powerhouse in email marketing service, you have an excellent opportunity to reach your audience and convince them through your targeted emails to become your client.\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel MailChimp add-on offers you the capability to collect emails from your potential customers and automate email campaign based on the nature of your leads. Integrating MailChimp with your travel agency website offers you the ability to segment your subscribers according to their behavior on your site and send them targeted emails to push them further into the conversion funnel.\\r\\n\\r\\nThis powerful MailChimp plugin for WordPress, allows you to send targeted emails along with sending periodic newsletters to your blog and season tour package offers to your subscribers. Emails are a great way to establish a long-term relationship and this WP Travel Plugin addon provides you all that you need for launching a successful email campaign.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Note:<\\/strong>\\r\\nThe WP Travel MailChimp add-on works only with <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/\\\">WP Travel Plugin<\\/a> \\u2013 the best WordPress Tour Booking Plugin for travel agency website on WordPress.\\r\\nThe WP Travel Plugin and the MailChimp add-on plugin are ONLY for travel and tour websites powered by WordPress.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Features of MailChimp WordPress plugin<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Unique forms for targeted segments<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nOne of the best features of this add-on is the ability to assign specific forms to specific MailChimp email campaign. The process is automatic in the website\\u2019s backend and once connected with the MailChimp account it syncs all the email lists with their respective email campaigns. Such a feature enables you to segment your users based on their interest and send targeted emails based on criteria such as click history or location.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Compliant with Anti-Spam Requirements<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis feature enables you to send verification and other emails which complies with anti-spam initiatives. With the built-in opt-in or opt-out feature, you can create the email which follows correct email marketing norms. It enables you to verify the validity of the email. And, it allows your user to choose the option to receive a periodic newsletter from you or to unsubscribe when they don\\u2019t want to, helping you to remain away from landing into their spam folder.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Automatic Routine Tasks<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWith this add-on, you can automate all the manual task by using pre-designed marketing strategies. Automated email marketing campaigns are one of the most important verticals in online marketing. With MailChimp automation features, this WP Travel MailChimp addon saves you a considerable amount of time by automating all the repeating task. Install this MailChimp add-on, set it up and focus on creating and optimizing strategy while it takes care of keeping your users informed and engaged.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Easy Integration<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nLike WP Travel, this addon is also very easy to install and use. With us doing all the backend coding and integration, you can just install and start configuring your travel agency backend with your MailChimp backend. You can even configure to sync all of the customer inquiries and booking emails to your MailChimp account and send out automated replies.\\r\\n\\r\\nGet into the action, start funneling your site visitors into potential customers by working on a strategic email campaign, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/themepalace.com\\/download-checkout\\/?edd_action=add_to_cart&amp;download_id=93576\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">download the WP Travel MailChimp Plugin Addon<\\/a> now. And click here for a <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-mailchimp\\/\\\">tutorial to install and setup WP Travel MailChimp plugin<\\/a>.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/mail-chimp-thumbnail.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2017,\n                        \"name\": \"Miscellaneous\",\n                        \"slug\": \"miscellaneous\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2017,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"15.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 6673,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-utilities\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Utilities\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-05-21 04:02:21\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-09-23 09:04:53\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=6673\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13557 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/wp-travel-utilities.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1649\\\" height=\\\"690\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Utilities is a bundle of basic features which enhances the WP travel plugin. The plugin basically addresses the minimal but important feature that is not available in the free version of WP Travel plugin. It lets you define your own custom trip code, enable\\/disable WP Travel \\\"Powered By Branding\\\" text or define your custom text. Likewise, it also has an option to send an email related to Trip Booking, Trip Payments and Trip Enquiry to your multiple recipients and more <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/downloads\\/wp-travel-utilities\\/#features\\\">features<\\/a>. WP Travel plugin must be installed and activated to use this addon. After you activate the plugin, a Utilities Option field will be added in the settings section of WP Travel plugin.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Features:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Multiple pricing checkout through single cart:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nMultiple pricing checkout allows the users to carry out the checkout process of a trip with multiple pricing ( e.g Adult , children, Infant and other ) through a single cart.\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-19678 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/backend-demo.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"656\\\" height=\\\"771\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center\\\">Screenshot : Back end view of multiple pricing single checkout feature<\\/p>\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-19679 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/frontend-demo.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"701\\\" height=\\\"499\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center\\\">Screenshot : Front end view of multiple pricing single checkout feature<\\/p>\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-19680\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/cart-page-veiw.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1146\\\" height=\\\"326\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center\\\">Screenshot : WP Travel Cart view of multiple pricing single checkout feature<\\/p>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Custom trip code:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Utilities let you customize and define your own custom trip code for your trips from the individual trip edit screen.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Powered by text remove:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThese options provide you to remove the Powered By text in the email template. You can either disable or enable the text or custom define your own text.\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Email Option<\\/b>:\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Utilities provides you options to add multiple email recipients for Trip booking, Trip payment, and Trip inquiry. You can send emails to multiple recipients using this option.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Custom tabs:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nAs a tour operator, you may want to publish more information about your trips so this plugin now allow to add custom tabs to trip. The tabs are displayed on the individual product pages to the right of the default \\u201cDescription\\u201d tab.\\r\\n<h4>FAQs:<\\/h4>\\r\\nThe FAQs feature will allow you to add the FAQs globally to every trip. The user will be able to add the FAQs from Settings &gt; FAQs. The FAQs added here will be available to all the trips.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/05\\/wp-travel-utilities-thumbnail.png\",\n                \"category\": false,\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"22.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 8351,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-tour-extras\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Tour Extras\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-10-30 07:51:33\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-02 10:45:23\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=8351\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12348 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/ws-travel-tour-extras_2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1920\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Tour Extras is a premium add-on which provides you the ability to add additional services to trip and tour packages. With this WP Travel plugin addon, you can add services like flight, vehicle service, insurance or any other customer service option in your site. Additionally, you can also add a gallery for the service, description and sale price.\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on enables you to create professional travel site with a load of additional facilities in your travel packages in just a few clicks. You can add unlimited additional services. You can inform your visitor by providing descriptive information on every travel package. With the intuitive and easy-to-use user interface, you can easily integrate this add-on in your site with no prior knowledge on programming.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe ability to provide customized extra options to the end users helps you to reach new audiences. All of your customers may not ask for the same services. As such, this add-on provides you the flexibility to cater to the needs of a wide range of customer by providing a combination of different services.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>NOTE:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>This Plugin is made for travel and trekking websites developed on WordPress<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin works ONLY with WP Travel Plugin \\u2013 the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\\">free tour operator and booking plugin for WordPress travel site.<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin comes integrated into the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-travel-pro\\/\\\">premium version of WP Travel Pro<\\/a> \\u2013 means you don\\u2019t have to purchase it standalone if you are WP Travel Pro user.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>Why you should install WP Travel Tour Extras Plugin<\\/strong>?\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Add extra facilities to your tour packages:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis feature allows you to provide additional services for specific tour and trip packages like flight, vehicle and other custom option you think are relevant to a travel package.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Mark Extra Services as Free or Paid w\\/ Prices:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWe understand that all additional services that are added to a package might not be free or paid. So we have provided the ability to mark them as Free and Paid services along with providing you the ability to set price for each of the additional services. Providing transparent information about charges is a good way to do business, so why not let your customers know how much they will have to pay if they want that additional service included in your package?\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Offer Discount on Extra Services<\\/strong> :\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add on helps you to provide special discounts on extra services as well. Offering discounted rates on additional services as part of the package helps you convey it to your potential clients the savings they will make if they get the trip package. This can be an additional boost to increase your sales.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Intuitive and easy front end UI:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Tour Extras is designed to be intuitive and easy to use while keeping your site healthy. The user interface is made appealing, easy and efficient, so the user can easily navigate through your site. And it is also intuitive and simple to apply so regardless of your programming skills you can create premium and professional travel website in hours by using the WP Travel plugin and its add-ons.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Extra Gallery:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on provides the feature of the Gallery section. With this feature, you\\u2019ll be able to create your custom galleries and display your image content to make your site even more appealing to visitors. This helps in creating and boosting your brand appeal while increasing the user engagement on the site- as images convey more than words can express!\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/10\\/wp-travel-tour-extras-thumbnail-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2017,\n                        \"name\": \"Miscellaneous\",\n                        \"slug\": \"miscellaneous\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2017,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"15.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 10243,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-field-editor\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Field Editor\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-02-06 10:11:53\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-09-23 09:14:44\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=10243\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13529 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/Banner.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"2910\\\" height=\\\"1162\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Field Editor add on provides the ability to add, edit, and remove a field in your travel package and itinerary pages while using the WP Travel plugin \\u2013 the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/\\\">best plugin for WordPress Travel websites<\\/a>. By installing this add on, you can boost your ability to add, edit and delete additional fields including fields for billing info, traveler info and trip inquiry form section making it easier for you to have as many fields as you want on the page.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhile this feature comes bundled in WP Travel Pro version, you will need to install this add on the free version of the plugin to have the ability to play around with fields. As a developer of a plugin and themes specially dedicated to travel agency websites on WordPress, we developed the Travel Field Editor add on to further boost your ability to do more on your travel website.\\r\\nThis add on makes your WP Travel plugin further customizable. You will have the ability to customize what field does and what doesn\\u2019t appear in your post and in what particular order. Here are some reasons why you should have it:\\r\\n<strong>Before You Proceed:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>The WP Travel Field editor requires the WP travel plugin to be installed, activated and configured.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Removing the core fields in your page may lead to the unexpected results sometimes.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>Core Features of WP Travel Field Editor:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Add a new custom field:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-13530\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/adding-new-field-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you want to add a new field in your travel form, easily do it by clicking on \\u201c+ Add file.\\u201d You can add custom fields in billing, traveler info and trip inquiry fields. The newly filled form contains options to provide values for Type, Name, Label, placeholder, validation and many more. With this fantastic user-oriented add on you can add new space for any information you want the user to fill in.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Edit field:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13531 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/edit-the-field-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWith field editor add-on you can edit the core and custom field in the billing, traveler info, and trip enquiry sections. You can have the option to provide new values for name, type. Label, text area validation, etc., in the edit form. This add-on is very much a handy tool when it comes to editing the form. Each form has its unique purpose to serve. You can edit the form by clicking the edit menu at the right.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Change field order:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-13532\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/change-field-order-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe add-on allows you to efficiently manage the display order of the checkout fields by using the drag and drop admin UI. Merely change the field order by moving fields up and down all you need to know is to move and click the mouse.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Remove field:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWell, you don\\u2019t need any fields on the form. No worries, you can go ahead and delete them straight away. Just click on the \\u201ccross\\u201d button at the right of the page.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Reset to factory setting:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nYes, you heard that right. This addon provides you the ability to reset your form fields to factory settings so that you can rebuild the form the way you want.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>How to Install the Addon?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe WP Travel Field editor only works with WP travel plugin. First, install and activate the WP Travel Plugin and integrate it with Field Editor. <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-field-editor\\/\\\">Click here<\\/a> to follow the installation tutorial.\\r\\n\\r\\nHave any questions, head on to our contact page and let us know your query. Always ready to help or want to some digging around, go on to our WP Field Editor forum pages.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/02\\/wp-travel-field-editor-logo.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2018,\n                        \"name\": \"Forms\",\n                        \"slug\": \"forms\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2018,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 1,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2017,\n                        \"name\": \"Miscellaneous\",\n                        \"slug\": \"miscellaneous\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2017,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"15.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 11475,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-partial-payment\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Partial Payment\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-03-06 10:33:50\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-02 10:18:59\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=11475\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-13522 size-full\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/partial_payment.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1497\\\" height=\\\"614\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nAre you looking for a WordPress booking partial payment plugin for a travel website? Then our WP Travel Partial Payment add on is the right choice for you. This is a plugin addon that works in sync with our main plugin WP Travel \\u2013 <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/\\\">the best free tour itinerary management plugin on WordPress.<\\/a> It allows your customer to pay for the trip package in installment and helps you keeping track of remaining amounts.\\r\\n\\r\\nThrough WordPress Partial Payment plugin, you can easily specify the partial payment plan of a trip while creating the package. So, the customer can book travel and tour package at specified installment cost and time. It can also be integrated with multiple payment gateways including PayPal, InstaMojo, PayStack, PayFast, Stripe, RazorPay, and Khalti (presently it does not support Authorize.Net). Providing the customer the flexibility to choose the payment gateway they prefer.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>NOTE:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>This WordPress Booking Partial Payment plugin is ONLY for Travel websites.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin works ONLY with WP Travel Plugin.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin comes integrated into the<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-travel-pro\\/\\\"> premium version of WP Travel Pro<\\/a> \\u2013 means you don\\u2019t have to purchase it standalone if you are WP Travel Pro user.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin does not a partial payment option for Authorize.Net payment gateway.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>How Does Partial Payment Help a Travel Website Generate More Business?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nMany travelers are not able to afford the full payment at once. They may be even uncertain and insecure about booking online travel and tour package. In such a situation, encouraging them to book the trip by providing partial payment option can help in increasing their confidence and ability to book the trip.\\r\\n\\r\\nCustomer may feel more comfortable to pay in installment. They can pay for a remaining portion of the payment in their own time. Partial payments can help you increase your conversion rate by reducing cart abandonment rates. By enabling the end user to have the ability to pay an installment, it increases interactions between the business owner and their customers.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe WP Travel Booking Partial Payment Plugin also helps site owner by sending reminder emails to customers of the due amount and provide them the ability to see their payment status in their dashboard. And when payment is completed, the end users are sent with a confirmation email. Such a transparent and seamless experience helps your business generate better business.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Why should you install this WordPress Booking Partial Payment Plugin on your Travel site?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>To Accept Partial Payment for Tour &amp; Trip Bookings<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on enables you to receive partial payment from your customer. The customer can pay for travel and tour package at the specified rate. You can set the installment rate and time for the trip while creating the package. So, the customer can choose the option of partial payment while checking out from a particular payment gateway. While they can pay for the remaining payment in installment basis. This feature provides flexibility in booking travel and tour package.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>To Send Automated Deposit Emails to end-users and admin<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on provides notification emails about the transaction. So, the customer can automatically track the amount that is left to be paid. When a purchase is made, the customer is notified about deposit amount and the remaining portion of the payment. And when the final amount is paid, email is sent to the customer about confirmation. It creates a smooth transition from one installment to another installment.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>For Clean Transaction Report<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nAll of the deposited payment made by the user is easily viewed in their respective tour booking dashboard. So, the customer can get the confirmation on every partial payment they made. The user can find details of the individual booking and details of the remaining amount from the dashboard. This feature helps the user and tour operator to make payment transparent and well informed. So, the user can be more confident about repeating the booking on your travel site.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>For Easy Integration With Your Travel Site<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on gives you complete access to the settings of the partial payment options. You can easily integrate this add-on in your WordPress site. It does not require you to write complicated code to use this add-on. You can customize the add-on according to the user need. And it can be easily used with any payment gateway. So, it gives you the option to collect partial payment from any payment gateways.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/partial_payment_thumbnail.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 166,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 166,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"19.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 5353,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-stripe-checkout\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Stripe Checkout\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-28 10:04:21\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-02 08:09:39\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=5353\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-12711\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/stripe-banner.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1500\\\" height=\\\"700\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">WP Travel Stripe WordPress Plugin add on is a payment plugin that helps you receive payments on WordPress travel site through Stripe. As one of the largest payment companies in the world, Stripe is a convenient way to accept online payments. It provides better user payment experience on every device including mobile, tablet and desktop. All the transactions are done on-site, and it allows you to provide one-time payment as well as recurring payment options for your customers. So, you don\\u2019t need to worry about losing a customer in an external page.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Running an online travel business can be an uphill battle if you have not integrated online payment modules like Stripe that work with a wide range of credit cards. Creating a strategic plan, engineering the best site that satisfies your customer needs and delivering them with a wide range of options to pay for the tour and trip bookings, can be very costly for your programmer to custom code it. So, we created this simple but powerful Stripe payment plugin for your travel site. When coupled with its parent travel plugin, WP Travel, this addon will further boost the growth of your travel business.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Stripe Checkout add-on is very easy to set up. You don\\u2019t need programming skills to integrate it on your site. Once you have merchant account on Stripe (which is also very easy), it requires very less time to integrate your website with your Stripe account. We have made the integration process very simple, saving your time with working with stripe php codes and all. It involves some drag and drops and some toggling with buttons to integrate. With this add-on, you can focus more on making better products and let it handle the payment part.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><b>Why Stripe Checkout WordPress plugin?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">WP Travel Stripe Payment Plugin is renowned for its safety features and ease of use for both customers and merchants. Stripe payment is famous as \\u201cPayment form done right\\u201d because of its seamless transaction experience to the customer all around the world.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">As an owner of a travel business, you can<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/dashboard.stripe.com\\/register\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\"> set up a Stripe merchant account<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\"> in just a few minutes. It has no setup fees, no monthly fees, and no hidden costs. It accepts all major debit and credit cards across the world, giving your would-be customers a wide array of choices to make the payment through.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Stripe Checkout is fully optimized for all sizes of mobile screens and the best site it works on your site \\u2013 without the user ever leaving it. The customer can pay instantly without being redirected away to payment gateway site. As such this provides you with the opportunity to upsell more products to these customers.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>What do you need to install the WP Travel Stripe Payment plugin?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Before installing the WP Travel Stripe Payment plugin on your site, you should create a Stripe merchant account. This is relevantly easy. In addition to that, you should install WP Travel plugin on the site as the Stripe payment plugin works ONLY with it. With these basics done, install the stripe payment plugin and follow onscreen instructions or i<\\/span><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-stripe-checkout\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">nstructions given here.<\\/span><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>NOTE:<\\/b>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">The WP Travel Payment plugin only works if the WP Travel plugin is installed.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">WP Travel is a plugin exclusively made for travel and tour agency WordPress websites.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Stripe works only pages with HTTPs connection.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><b>WP Travel Stripe Payment Plugin Features:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Frictionless Onsite Checkout:<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">WP Travel Stripe Payment plugin add-on offers the ability to have single page checkout for your customers. Nothing is frustrating than going to multiple pages to pay. Users simply hate this, as we do. With this option, visitors can quickly click on the stripe payment button and make the payment without leaving your site. As such it helps to decrease the shopping cart abandonment rates and increase the volume of trip bookings.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Highly Secured <\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">This Stripe payment plugin uses the Stripe API that provides a highly secure environment for the users to make the transaction. It comes loaded with Stripe Radar, fraud protection tools along with other security features. It helps in detecting and preventing fraud along with counterfeit transactions. Stripe uses advanced machine learning infrastructure that allows it to identify shifting fraud patterns and control them constantly.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Wide range of debit and credit card options<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">The Stripe Payment plugin allows your users to pay for your trips and tour bookings using Stripe account or their debit and credit cards. This add-on accepts most of the debit and credit card. You can easily prompt them to enter the credit card number. It provides real-time feedback. So your visitor can easily identify error while filling stripe forms.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Highly customizable settings<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">The WP Travel Stripe Payment plugin is engineered to allow customization to checkout form and add custom fields. As such, no matter what your website\\u2019s design or color scheme is, you can adapt Stripe checkout forms to it. This helps to maintain consistent branding on your website. The UI toolkit provided by Stripe gives collective experience for the front end and design. You can easily access the setting page from your WordPress site.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Built-in mobile support (Responsive)<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Our Stripe Checkout WordPress plugin has built-in mobile support. It automatically adapts to mobile devices. This checkout lets your customers save their time by providing easy navigation in mobile devices. It adjusts to the different screen sizes of the mobile, tablet and desktop.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Power your tour and travel agency website with the all-in-one solution, WP Travel, and boost your abilities to receive online payment through Stripe today. Download it now.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/05\\/stripe-checkout.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 166,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 166,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2670,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Payment Plugins &amp; Gateways For Travel &amp; Tour Websites\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-travel-site-payment-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2670,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"<strong>Payment Plugins for WordPress Travel Sites<\\/strong>\\r\\nAbility to accept online payment is an important feature of the modern businesses. This is crucial for business that cater to worldwide audiences, like travel and tour sites. Having the ability for the user to instantly pay for their travel and tour bookings can be a great feature for the end users to use. And for the business, this could mean getting paid by users and getting real paid customers. But for developers or site owners integrating even the widely available payment gateways like PayPal, Authorize.net, can be a serious pain.\\r\\n\\r\\nAt WP Travel, we take this pain out of your schedule. We offer plugins for most of the widely used payment gateways around the world. These WordPress payment plugins are EXCLUSIVELY developed to work with WP Travel and are ONLY for travel and tour websites built on WordPress. Here are some of our most popular payment plugins for travel and tour websites on WordPress:\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>PayPal Checkout WordPress Plugi